Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After setting out to establish\Na route to Shiganshina,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the Scout Regiment encountered\Nan intelligent, female Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As soldier after soldier fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the regiment rushed\Ninto a forest of giant trees,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,much to everyone's puzzlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who can possibly stop it,\Nif not the Levi Squad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We could've saved him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you trust yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,or me, these guys,\Nand the entire Scout Regiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to take that Titan alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of that, Eren?!\NWe caught that Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the might of the Scout Regiment!\NDon't underrate us, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now do you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't drop our guard yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just impressed you\Nmanaged to lead her to this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The credit goes to the rear squad\Nmembers who gave their lives fighting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They bought us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been impossible otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...we get to see who's\Ninside this one's nape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just hope they're not\Nwetting themself inside there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let your deaths be meaningless{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even if I'm the last one standing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In both hands, Gloria{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What sings is Sieg{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On my back, Flügel der Freiheit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clenched determination to my left chest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What slashes across is Linie der Torheit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soaring across the azure skies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flügel der Freiheit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Erwin Smith"\N"The 57th Exterior Scouting Mission, Part 4"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An Abnormal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it like the Colossal Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did Commander Erwin actually--?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Quit spacin' out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can think later!\NWe need to get further ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Levi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be extra cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Waves 2 and 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the reserves too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, they're starting to climb up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If they make it up this far,\Nperhaps I'll step out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect we'll soon be given\Norders to withdraw anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it have something to do\Nwith those explosions inside the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think those sounds are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are cannons being\Nfired inside the forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't {\i1}see {\i0}them bring\Nany cannons in, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all this damn noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Bertholdt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know which way Christa went?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing makes sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we even doing now, and why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let's move away, Armin!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the bastard's\Ngotten the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten better and\Nbetter at tree-climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The scary thing is that\Nthis means they can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm sure it's\Ndifferent for each Titan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be up to\Nsomething inside the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think I've\Nfigured out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They lured that female Titan here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, more precisely,\Nto capture the human inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Commander Erwin's goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I can understand keeping\Nit from us rookies, but you guys too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been Scouts a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting the commander\Nand the captain don't trust us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, but that's what\Nthis means, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Petra! Knock out his teeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch his front teeth with his back ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Eren's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain must've had a\Nreason for not trusting us implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one reason\Nhe couldn't trust his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in the regiment\Nwho can either turn into a Titan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or is working as a sort of spy for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so too, right?\NThat there's someone in the regiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. I think there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least,\Nthe commander must believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume the only soldiers\Ninformed of this operation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,were the ones who survived five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's gotta be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it, Eren?\NThat's what's goin' on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. In that case, it couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago\Nwas when the wall first fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they be using that\Nfact to narrow down suspects
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,on the assumption\Nthat's when the spy got inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean this person\Nkilled Sawney and Bean too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The commander asked me\Nsomething after that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you {\i0}see here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think the enemy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is {\i1}that {\i0}what that meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We might've been allowed\Nto join the operation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if we'd known the answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt any of us could have, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I decided not to say anything.\NDo you guys know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you mean you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess guys like\Nyou wouldn't know, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nowhere near my\Nlevel yet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, are you still\Ntrying to imitate Captain Levi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If this succeeds, we might actually\Nlearn the truth about this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, even for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...way too many people have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the commander\Nwas wrong to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the right,\NI'll tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we'd actually been told\Nthat a Titan had inside info,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we would've handled things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own squad members, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--No, it wasn't wrong.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many\Nsoldiers have needlessly died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In hindsight, it's easy to\Nsay what should've been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can tell how things will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, at some point\Nyou {\i1}have {\i0}to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives of a hundred comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...or the lives of\Neveryone inside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The commander chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He chose to throw away\Nthe lives of a hundred comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't know already,\Nyou'll soon learn why
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin Smith was put in charge\Nof the Scouts, of humanity's hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's why he even\Nhas Captain Levi's trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's assuming you\Nsurvive long enough, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much\Nlife experience yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I {\i1}do {\i0}know one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone who\Ncan bring about change,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's someone capable of\Ngiving up what matters most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In particular, people who are capable\Nof abandoning their humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when forced to rise above monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who can't abandon anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...can't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can't scratch a\Nsingle itch or move a single muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And you probably never will again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The more your wounds heal,\Nthe stiffer your joints will get!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, why haven't they\Nextracted our esteemed guest yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are Levi and Miche doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So she has the ability to cover portions\Nof her body with hardened skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:12:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Much like the Armored Titan I've heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it weaken if we continue\Nan ODM sword assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In which case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to blast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow off the target's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a\Nrisk our standard artillery
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,could take out everything\Non the inside as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's attempt to\Nsever the wrists instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire an all-out salvo on my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Just come out already, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't got time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what do you think's\Ngonna happen to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you\Ncan get out of this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd pay some thought\Nto the trouble you've caused us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed our men in\Nall sorts of different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I'm {\i0}having fun now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you're the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone who\Nknows how I feel, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be fine if\Nyour limbs get cut off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll go grow back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about your {\i1}actual {\i0}body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't afford to have\Nyou die on us, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. You startled me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Were those her death throes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin. I smell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Which direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All directions, all at once!\NLots of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!\NThey're rushing into the forest all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they suddenly ignoring us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean they're {\i1}all {\i0}Abnormals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter! Don't let 'em through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard screams like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In the forest where I'm from!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the sound a cornered animal makes\Nwhen it's ready to give up everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was taught the end of a hunt\Nis when you have to be most careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want me to be careful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be a hundred times\Nmore careful than normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will {\i0}die if you\Ndon't take the forest seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the mountains too, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a vegetable farmer!\NYou wouldn't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha's hunches {\i1}are {\i0}often right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's usually only before\Nsomething bad happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin said Eren might be in the\Nrear of the center rank, as I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry with artillery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The first wave is coming\Nfrom the east! They're close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wagon defense squad! Intercept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're ignoring us?!\NAre they Abnormals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Titans have broken through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You just did something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It went for the female one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans coming from all directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers, commence combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Defend the Female Titan at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All soldiers, withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Redeploy the formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to Calaneth District!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been bested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that pathetic look of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This goes to show that the enemy\Nwas prepared to throw away everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined our target\Nwould resort to Titan cannibalization
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to dispose of information...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After all that blustering we did\Nin the courtroom, this is how it turns out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If we waltz back there now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows what'll happen to Eren or us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can think about that once we've returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we need to focus on returning\Nwithout sustaining any further losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The steam is impairing visibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It could hinder smoke signal communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Levi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Replenish your gas and blades first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're low on time and\NI have enough to last already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order. Do as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, Erwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll trust your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The withdrawal signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all to withdraw and\Nreturn to base on horseback.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is it all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Eren all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to the\Nhorses! Prepare to withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see what the\Nbastard riding inside it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they really find out who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You trusted us, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Things turned out this way\Nbecause you chose to stick with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Making the right call is a pretty\Nhard thing to do, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. Quit pamperin' him, Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How was {\i1}he {\i0}any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All he did was whine\Nlike a pathetic little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess making it back alive {\i1}might{\i0}\Nbe considered praiseworthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but only after the\Nmission's done and over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, twerp, an expedition\Nain't over 'til you're back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oruo! Petra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For a couple of soldiers who cried and\Npissed their pants during their first battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you've really grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}trying {\i0}to make\Nhim lose respect for me, Eld?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she really did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And, just so you know,\NI never pissed myself, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! I'll have you know\NI have the highest kill count!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the best, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to a soldier's\Nmerits than just kill counts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Petra! Does that mean\Nit sprayed everywhere in midair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on a picnic or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're outside the walls, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I never wet myself either, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That must be a\Nmessage from Captain Levi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're rendezvousing with the captain!\NStow the chatter until we're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Erwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have\NLevi replenish his supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when there's no time to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The female was eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But did you see the\Nperson inside get eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If, as you deduced earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we're dealing with a type that remains\Nable-bodied after de-transformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And, if said person had equipped\Nthemselves with ODM gear in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...that means they're now\Nwearing one of our uniforms...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Levi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Gunther!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gunther!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...and have blended in\Nwith the rest of us soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If, by chance, I'm not me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then who's to say that you're you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you pick up the pieces of your heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that fell apart like a broken sand castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The voice of someone calling out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}changed into ringing in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's as if time has stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now wake up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made my way out of the deep darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fled like a swift wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We used to be like living corpses,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now we head beyond the walls{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's meet again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a place not on any map{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,0:24:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The capture operation has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Female Titan appears\Nbefore Eren once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing in the way is a\Nteam of Titan-killing experts...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Special Operations Squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Crushing Blow"\N"The 57th Exterior Scouting Mission, Part 5"
